1.title: Style Hunt
1.plot: Paula Garces takes you behind the scenes of Wisin & Yandel's latest video. Resident stylist Jorge Ramon shows you how to get Gwen Stefani's look for less. Jenni Rivera takes Paula shopping in L.A. and Kat Von D shows how to get a tattoo look without the needle. Plus, a mun2 viewer gets the makeover of a lifetime.

2.title: Accessories
2.plot: Paula shows us how to take a plain outfit and make it pop with cool accessories. We hang out 50 Cent in Los Angeles for the launch of his cologne "Power by 50 Cent." Wilmer Valderrama invites Paula into his home to make arepas and talk about Wilmer's very accessorized style. Plus, we go behind the scenes of Paula's cover shoot for "Latino Future" magazine and Detroit Piston, Charlie Villanueva, gives a breakdown of his look.

3.title: All About Men
3.plot: This time it's all about the guys! Paula goes riding on ATV's with Wisin & Yandel, Pitbull takes us backstage at his New York City concert to talk style and Marcy Place get hot new looks. Left coast regional Mexican producers Los Twiins show us their controversial new clothing line ANVEM. This week's viewer makeover is Christian, who wants to go from the hood to business class - that means getting his first haircut in 12 years!

4.title: Date Night
4.plot: Paula sits down with romantic bachatero Romeo from Aventura. He gives the lowdown on his style and what he likes in the ladies. We go backstage at Fashion week to check out the runway shows and interview Mexican designer Luca Luca. On the Left Coast, we link up with jewelry designer Melody Ehsani who has created jewelry pieces for every major female star out from Mariah Carey to Beyonce to Keri Hilson. Jorge answers your questions and gives the audience a tip on how to wear Metallic dresses ala Eva Mendes. Paula preps for a hot date and shows our audience what she ...

5.title: Shoes
5.plot: Kat DeLuna goes shopping for shoes with Paula Garces in New York while Fabolous reveals his obsession with sneakers. We get a sneak peek of all the upcoming styles and trends at one of the biggest shoe expos to hit New York City - FFANY. On the Left Coast, we check out Barracuda, a store/salon/party location in Los Angeles founded by Mexico City pro-skater Miguel de la Barracuda. Plus, Jorge helps mun2 viewer Ashley go from Catholic school girl to girly glamor.

6.title: Fashion Emergencies
6.plot: Daddy Yankee shows off his style, Paula hangs out with Dania Ramirez to talk movies and fashion and we go behind the scenes of the Carmen Marc Valvo runway show to see what it's like to be a fashion model. Then we head to downtown Los Angeles to meet up with famed tattoo artist Mr. Cartoon, who just came out with his own Casio G-shock watch. Paula shows you how to take care of fashion emergencies that happen on the go. This week's makeover is Gracie, a "hoochie" who wants to be taken seriously at work. Can Jorge give her a touch of class while still keeping her sexy? ...

7.title: Travel Essentials: Puerto Rico
7.plot: Paula Garces takes you on a trip to Puerto Rico, where she shows you travel essentials that work for any hot and sexy vacation. Flex joins Paula for a lesson in "Romantic Style," LMFAO are in L.A. with a new clothing line, and Paula joins Ivy Queen to get a special spa treatment. Jorge Ramon helps Ann with a much-needed makeover.

8.title: I've Been Invited
8.plot: Flex and Taboo from the Black Eyed Peas show off their looks. Snoop breaks down his doggy style. Mario Lopez tells us how he gets those great abs. Paula takes us behind the scenes of her hit Syfy show Warehouse 13. Jorge Ramon takes a viewer through fashion boot-camp.

9.title: Beauty
9.plot: Kimora Lee Simmons presents Baby Phat's latest fragrance, Dare Me. Taboo (Black Eyed Peas) gives Paula an up close and personal look at his new sneaker line for Jump. Cosculluela and Ivy Queen show off their street styles. Check out a Los Angeles shop where all your favorite bandas get suited up.

10.title: Little Black Dress
10.plot: Enrique Iglesias gives us the scoop on the look for his latest album. Tito El Bambino breaks down his estilo. Paula interviews Machete star, Danny Trejo. Jorge helps a mun2 viewer accessorize her office look. Paula takes the little black dress from season to season.

11.title: Jeans for Everyone
11.plot: Paula Garcés finds out how corrido king Larry Hernandez stays fly. RKM & Ken-Y break down their estilo. Race car driver Milka Duno takes us to the track. Stylist to the stars Ken Paves shows you how to work hair extensions. Jorge Ramon gives tips on how to look like the hottest celebrities for less.

12.title: Girl's Night Out
12.plot: Jencarlos Canela takes us inside his dressing room on the set of his new music video. Pop singer Belinda breaks down her style. Nelly Furtado tells Paula Garcés what really inspires her. Paula and her home-girls get you ready for a night out on the town. Jorge Ramon shares celebrity style tips and gives a rocker chick a classed-up makeover.
